{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main character of the game is a professional barista who is forced by chance to become a bartender. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help him become successful in this craft! Visit different establishments to learn new recipes, meet people in the industry and learn their skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/extras/Ready-Mix-Shake-Blend.gif?t=1738670071\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only your skills will determine how successful you are in making and serving a variety of cocktails correctly and on time. Will you be able to keep up with the fast pace? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Develop your own tactics as the chaotic game unfolds. Use hints or come up with your own strategies to deliver orders quickly with minimal movement and interaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/extras/BartenderRunsWithBillsNoBackground.gif?t=1738670071\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Faster is better, but don't forget to keep an eye on quality. After all, the wrong ingredients will result in garbage. The happier your customers are, the better your feedback and the more stars you can earn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only your actions will determine the end of this story!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738670071","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738670071","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/2787c41853eae7e6d277539cbea5894ec2571711/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738670071","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113670/2787c41853eae7e6d277539cbea5894ec2571711/capsule_184x6